The main strategy of Vodafone in this area is in the search for a partner to build a shared network for a fast mobile Internet."
The responsible authorities - hand in hand with the providers
The action of mobile radio providers is easy to understand that another provider called more competition, this would lead to lower prices and thus also to a fall in profits.
