Some children speak at night
I mean not those who wake up and tell us something that happened the day before, but the children who speak during sleep.
If it happens to you for the first time, in the best case you will be shocked, but in reality this has no significance.
This is a positive sleep disturbance called the talk in sleep.
She is quite widespread, especially in children and adolescents.
Surely, more than one of you were told that you talked at night.
This phenomenon may occur occasionally (one time in life, for example, during the high fever), or regularly (every day, once a week, once a month), the child can remember nothing the next day.
There is no single reason that causes this appearance.
There are often links with other appearances in sleep, such as nightmares, panic anxiety at night, Enuresis noctura (bedding at night), talking in sleep, but there is no reason for it.
As we mentioned earlier, it can be due to very high fibers, stress situations or overload.
In any case, this is a little researched phenomenon.
